                <img src="\imj\watch1.jpg" alt="Slider Image 4">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="slider-content">
            <p>
                Welcome to Stigma, your one-stop shop for all your male product needs. We offer a wide range of
                high-quality products designed for men.
            </p>
